channel.description: Talking Points Memo is a political blog founded by Josh Marshall during the 2000 U.S. presidential election. Since then, TPM has expanded its coverage of U.S. political news with new content from TPMmuckraker, TPMDC, TPMLiveWire, TPMIdeaLab, TPM2012 and TPMPollTracker. Talking Points Memo's YouTube channel features content from its newest project, TPMtv.
channel.title: tpmtv
